g Tây Sơn kiểm sát sứ Đậu thị ngự - 入奏行贈西山檢察使竇侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-wwxs7iJe3IRK6mSsXfh_gQ">Thảo đường - 草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%8B-t%C3%B2ng-t%C3%B4n-T%E1%BA%BF/poem-IT-lvhqSGw2uNWQEoMNJqQ">Thị tòng tôn Tế - 示從孫濟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C6%AF%E1%BB%9Bc/T%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-IXu-MXCYKr5ugEOxUvHmLw">Tòng quân hành kỳ 3 - 從軍行其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C6%AF%E1%BB%9Bc/author-QsX6zPvNLkl8nV5t-1mhuw">Lý Ước</a>)<br></div>	</div>
